      • CODA_WARN

        public static final int CODA_WARN
        CODA_WARNING msg, 9. Will show up on RC gui as orange. Technically it's an error, but used as a warning when component state does not need to be changed, but error condition exists.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • SEVERE
